commentPostTextItems.html: This was a do or die match for the Indians, they have done well to beat Sri Lanka for the second consecutive match
Sri Lanka were set a  stiff target of 228 for a win. Zaheer Khan and Nehra bowled well to destroy the top-rder
Tomorrow's match between India and New Zealand is a virtual semi final. The winners will go to the finals on the 05th of August.
CricInfo's Top Performer of the day is Yuvraj Singh for his brilliant knock of 98 not out
Sri Lanka batsmen put up a below par performance with the bat and were bowled out for just 181.
Tomorrow is the big game. India will take on New Zealand, it is going to be a cracker of a match
Yuvraj Singh is the Man of the Match
We will be back with you tomorrow with all the live action at 1000 Hrs local time, 0930 Hrs IST, 0400 Hrs GMT. Thanks for being with us.
